{"tid":789310,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"個個咁想樓價跌，講到尾就係自己想買樓。","createTime":"2018-08-22T07:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T10:10:25.000Z","uid":103799,"like":47,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7e4d84cb7434f3fa9c1de079920295bbd0b169","tid":789310,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"97果時個個都係想升，個個睇升，按上按，所以一跌個個攪唔掂。<br />\n<br />\n18年，而家個個都捕住個樓價，郁小小就話大跌。其實因為心入面個個都等緊回調想買樓，買樓住又好，收租又好。<br />\n咁多人捕住想買樓你同我講樓價會大跌?"},{"pid":"246eeffb70fd8d97bfd19f28377f73a6e398cc49","tid":789310,"uid":44698,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"所以咪話淡淡正仆街囉<br />\n明明自己想買又冇能力<br />\n要人地仆街成全佢地"},{"pid":"486e1f0d64ed2a9c643df59187fb2da44445d34e","tid":789310,"uid":45518,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"淡淡<br />\n利申: 有樓"},{"pid":"604d5634a4c11db43c90fa5773776525d923461f","tid":789310,"uid":192589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"炒唔係攞黎炒架"},{"pid":"469dfe44747b0eecea05ef05e98b7f0ceb952a40","tid":789310,"uid":55924,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:24:42.000Z","msg":"全世界得港人咁撚賤<br />\n想買樓竟然被人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75434dd64f78d010a72f3f73aeb4970240235ef2","tid":789310,"uid":57424,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:31:21.000Z","msg":"如果政府比公屋 居屋 首置我, 我話之你一億一CM呀仆街<br />\n炒貴哂D樓又輸唔起<br />\n你咁講同你有絕証, 得一隻藥醫, 但隻藥用黎炒比得起先有得食, 明明無病都黎炒, 有咩分別"},{"pid":"80570e9a2f4911fef21af00c161beed4a7886971","tid":789310,"uid":48889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"係 但想知想買樓有咩問題"},{"pid":"fc4ba1c129fcfce2b105ee244331945ccec786d1","tid":789310,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66d5468520a7bd17e4306bbbcf5f0659919f7007","ti